foods.ingredients: CHEESE: LOW MOISTURE PART SKIM MOZZARELLA CHEESE (CULTURED PASTEURIZED PART SKIM MILK, SALT, ENZYMES). SAUCE: WATER, TOMATO PASTE, MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SUGAR, SALT, SPICES (INCLUDING OREGANO), MALTODEXTRIN, DEXTROSE, GARLIC AND ONION, CITRIC ACID, GUAR GUM, BEET POWDER, EXTRACTIVE OF PAPRIKA. ASIAGO: (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, AND ENZYMES), POWDERED CELLULOSE (TO PREVENT CAKING). SPICE BLEND: SPICES (OREGANO, PEPPER, BASIL), MALTODEXTRIN, ONION & GARLIC, SOYBEAN OIL, PARSLEY. ULTRA THIN CRUST: ENRICHED FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, ENZYME, FOLIC ACID), WATER, SOYBEAN OIL, YEAST, DEXTROSE, CALCIUM PROPIONATE (PRESERVATIVE), OLIVE OIL, SALT, DOUGH CONDITIONER (SODIUM METABISULFITE) AND SOY LECITHIN.
